Rules:

Folder name must contain "histopath"

Magnification folders like 10x, 20x, 40x

Supported formats: .jpg .jpeg .png .tif .tiff

 Installation
1. Python

Python â‰¥ 3.8

2. Tkinter (GUI Library)
Ubuntu / Debian
sudo apt-get install python3-tk

RHEL / CentOS
sudo yum install tkinter

Arch
sudo pacman -S tk

macOS
brew install python-tk

Windows

Bundled by default. Verify:

python -m tkinter

3. Pillow (Image Handling)
pip install pillow

 How to Run
Windows - Execute RUN_Histopath_labeller.exe 
Executable on Linux using wine. 

Terminal Based Run - 
python3 histopath_label_tool.py


Workflow:

Select Dataset Root

Select Output CSV

Enter Annotator Name

Start Labelling

Grade + Comment

Auto summary & audit file generated

